cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CVPR 

This paper deals with depth estimation using convolutional neural networks and LiDAR data for self-driving cars. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves robotics (cs.RO) as it deals with self-driving cars. The use of neural networks for depth estimation also falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper mentions the KITTI dataset, which is commonly used in computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CVPR) research.
